
# LinkedIn Job Details Chrome Extension

## Description

This Chrome extension dynamically fetches and displays job details from LinkedIn job pages. It updates the displayed information when the user selects a different job on the page, providing an efficient way to view key job details without leaving the current page.

## Features

- Fetches job details such as location, job type, role, and description.
- Dynamically updates the displayed information when a new job is selected.
- Easy to install and use.

## Installation

1. **Download the ZIP file**: [LinkedInJobDetailsExtension.zip](https://drive.google.com/file/d/14AlbqCTpKbqs1i2u9kX3Oh1GUWx1f79e/view?usp=sharing)

2. **Extract the ZIP file**:
   - Download the ZIP file from the provided link.
   - Extract the contents to a folder on your computer.

3. **Load the extension in Chrome**:
   - Open Chrome and go to `chrome://extensions/`.
   - Enable "Developer mode" by toggling the switch on the top right.
   - Click on the "Load unpacked" button.
   - Select the extracted folder from step 2.
   - The extension will now be added to Chrome.

## Usage

1. **Navigate to LinkedIn Jobs**:
   - Open LinkedIn and go to the Jobs section (e.g., [LinkedIn Jobs Page](https://www.linkedin.com/jobs/collections/recommended/?currentJobId=4061295956)).

2. **Activate the Extension**:
   - Click on the extension icon in the Chrome toolbar.
   - The extension will display job details from the current LinkedIn job page.

3. **View Job Details**:
   - When you select a different job on the LinkedIn job page, the extension will automatically update the displayed details.

